snippet.title: Chronoshot - RFLXT Studio Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Chronoshot is a free-to-play sci-fi arena shooting game, with specialized time mechanics. It will be the first game to utilize RFLXT's platform features, and is launching soon in Early Access Open Beta on both RFLXT and Epic Games. 

Wishlist on Epic at https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/chronoshot-4b6a41

Follow RFLXT at... 

Twitter (X) - https://twitter.com/rflxtstudio
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/rflxtstudio/ 
Discord - https://discord.gg/afpd6wduUF


Chronoshot is published by RFLXT, and developed by iMotion Pictures, Inc.
